{"tid":1096717,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍批准雷神公司簽訂新合約 台北設愛國者飛彈防禦系統","createTime":"2019-04-08T01:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T01:59:00.000Z","uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"21d8c22d339706ac662675de28046594460cacfc","tid":1096717,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190408/640_a9cfa23d3a71fb95a0fc426175253701.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190408%2F640_a9cfa23d3a71fb95a0fc426175253701.jpg&h=cdb6f4c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n花蓮基地展示的愛國者飛彈。資料照片<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部日前宣布，雷神公司（Raytheon）已獲准簽訂價值近2.8億台幣合約，要在台北佈署愛國者飛彈防禦系統。<br />\n美國國防部本月4日在官網上宣布，製造愛國者飛彈防禦系統的雷神公司已獲得一項價值903.5萬美元（約2.8億元台幣）外國軍售合約，要在台灣台北設置飛彈防禦系統。<br />\n<br />\n根據該項公告，此愛國者飛彈防禦系統將在2024年4月3日前佈署完成。<br />\n軍事新聞網站「Defense Blog」報導，自2015年1月起，在全球各地佈署的愛國者飛彈攔截系統已成功攔截逾百枚來襲飛彈。雷神公司迄今已製造超過220枚愛國者飛彈，並將其運送至16國客戶手中。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190408/1546790/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190408%2F1546790%2F&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUQFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=8e04173b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190408%2F1546790%2F&h=4c422239\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190408/1546790/</a>"},{"pid":"54baab865311add5e1330505a19309bbd35ef9b3","tid":1096717,"uid":202412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:48:20.000Z","msg":"7000萬港紙<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"694c5a53985a2323f40ec431f92459f61dad6938","tid":1096717,"uid":57376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:50:32.000Z","msg":"2024年<br />\n咁就要睇下台灣發咗大財未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /